OL,3,CSchool cancels plans for 'blue nosed
OL,4,Cday' after concerns from parents
OL,6,FA school in County Durham has
OL,7,Fcancelled plans to turn the heating
OL,8,Foff for a whole day this week in a bid
OL,9,Fto reduce its carbon footprint
OL,10,Ffollowing concerns from parents.
OL,12,FWolsingham Secondary School had
OL,13,Fplanned to hold a "Blue Nose Day" on
OL,14,FFriday to save energy and highlight to
OL,15,Fpupils the importance of being more
OL,16,Fsustainable.
OL,18,FOn Tuesday, the state school said the
OL,19,Fevent would no longer go ahead as
OL,20,Fplanned after "speaking to several
OL,21,Fparents regarding their concerns".
