OL,3,CSchool cancels plans for 'blue nosed
OL,4,Cday' after concerns from parents
OL,6,FIn a letter to parents, Wolsingham
OL,7,FSchool said the heating would be
OL,8,Fswitched on as normal on Friday and
OL,9,Fstaff and pupils would no longer need
OL,10,Fto wear extra layers of clothing.
OL,12,FIt added that students in the climate
OL,13,Faction team will now plan for the
OL,14,F"Blue Nose Day" event to go ahead in
OL,15,Fthe summer term next year instead of
OL,16,Fthe middle of October.
