OL,3,CSchool cancels plans for 'blue nosed
OL,4,Cday' after concerns from parents
OL,6,FThe letter sent to parents and carers
OL,7,Fof pupils from Wolsingham School on
OL,8,FTuesday said: "The event was designed
OL,9,Fto raise the importance in our school
OL,10,Fcommunity of being more sustainable
OL,11,Fand in a small way reduce the school's
OL,12,Fcarbon footprint.
OL,14,F"The date was carefully chosen by
OL,15,Flooking at average temperatures by
OL,16,Fmonth and short-term weather
OL,17,Fforecasts, indicating a temperature in
OL,18,FWolsingham of approx. 15C on Friday.
