OL,3,CSchool cancels plans for 'blue nosed
OL,4,Cday' after concerns from parents
OL,6,F"After careful consideration and
OL,7,Fspeaking to several parents regarding
OL,8,Ftheir concerns, the Blue Nose Day
OL,9,Fscheduled for Friday October 18 2024
OL,10,Fwill now not go ahead as planned.
OL,12,F"School will be open as usual with
OL,13,Fstaff and students not needing to wear
OL,14,Fextra layers of clothing and with the
OL,15,Fheating switched on as on a normal
OL,16,Fschool day.
