OL,3,CSchool cancels plans for 'blue nosed
OL,4,Cday' after concerns from parents
OL,6,F"Students in the climate action team
OL,7,Fhave already played a key part in
OL,8,Fmaking Wolsingham School more
OL,9,Fsustainable in other ways over the
OL,10,Flast few academic years.
OL,12,F"This includes the installation of
OL,13,Ffiltered water coolers, meaning the
OL,14,Famount of single use plastic, from
OL,15,Fwater bottles, has been reduced to
OL,16,Fextremely close to zero.
